summary: Bright White Pentagon shaped lights , really high in the sky directly above me
stats: Occurred : 5/4/2019 02:51  (Entered as : 05/04/2019 2:51 AM) Reported: 11/28/2022 6:05:17 PM 18:05 Posted: 12/22/2022 Location: Palm Bay, FL Shape: Circle Duration: 30sec Characteristics: There were lights on the object, There was an aura or haze around the object, The object changed color
text:
Bright White Pentagon shaped lights , really high in the sky directly above me 
 
I had just had a horrible breakup a month or 2 before and I was thinking about really dark thoughts. I was walking on my front lawn, towards my front door and a bright and expanding light got my attention. ( I usually like to find constellations on a clear night before going home). In person I could see a pentagon shape of a white lights focused in at a single point expanding slowly, and I believe rotating, after 6-8 seconds it seemed to either explode or disperse. The moment I noticed I got my iPhone out to record within 2 seconds of noticing. ( I like to document my life). I have not edited or done anything to the video except take 2 screenshots. I have no idea what it could be, one thing I‚Äôll note, I usually watch the , SpaceX boosters come back at night and day, Artemis and shuttle launches, and I can confirm I have not Seen ANYTHING. Like. This. Before. I went from being heartbroken that night, to wondering wtf just happened. If I were to guess the altitude I was looking at, it was very high in the atmosphere, similar to when a booster or other large object falls through atmosphere, but I have never, ever seen such a perfect pentagon expand from a single white bright point, evenly expand like this. This truly shook me and I am barely getting around to tell people now. Let me know if this is really something. It went from white, to Light blue. Odd thing is, when a booster falls through the atmosphere at night, usually at that altitude you see light from the setting sun above the lower atmosphere reflecting light off the trail, but I‚Äôve never seen light at that altitude glow past midnight. We‚Äôre usually fully in the earths shadow by 2am. The video has geolocation, time and shot on iPhoneXR. Went from 5 lights, to 3, then 2. Then just slowly faded. 
Facing North/ almost directly over me. occurred at Old address: 591 ortega st Palm bay Fl, 32909

2019 late october around 1. 30 am i was cleaning our farm shed out as i couldnt sleep because i was taking care of a sick brother getting worse from a brain tumor so i decided to strip our shed out through the night while he finally went to sleep, while i was taking a leak near our cars in the driveway out of know where in the area i was pissing were these beams of lights around me, i looked down and around me first and said where the fk did they come from then looked up and about 30 to 40 feet above me shining over me, and moving real slow ,about slow walking speed ,this what ever it was floating over me.I thought might be a helicopter but it was to close and didnt even make a sound and was way to big to be a drone ,floated over and past me and stopped about 20 feet away as if it looked like it was watching me , it was about the size of our 25000 litre water tank and while it was resting there i saw another one either come out of it or it was behind it and that one shot off heading towards our township in a split second and disappeared the main one stayed for about another minute and in one or two seconds shot up towards the night sky and vanished ,I wasnt scared of it while i was watching it , I was so amazed I saw a ufo or what ever it was ,its something you dont forget .It wasnt an orb because it was to big ,but I did want to know what was flying this thing , it was real fast and noiseless ,its no wonder any military cant catch these things ,the way they took off ,the governments might get lucky now elon musks has and is still putting sateites all over our planet or if another one crashes,but i am so wrapped I saw these ones , the next day i checked the roof of my car for burns as i didnt feel any burn marks on myself .so still here and still alive ,but was brassed off ,20 metres away my bloody mobile was in the kitchen, so there is something out there and i want to know what , newzealand see"s a few objects up there ,wrapped i found this site

summary: UFO outside house (only seen from inside) abduction through walls/roof (?)
stats: Occurred : 11/9/2019 00:00  (Entered as : 11/09/2019 12:00 AM) Reported: 12/21/2022 12:11:39 AM 00:11 Posted: 12/22/2022 Location: Havre de Grace, MD Shape: Unknown Duration: unkown.30mins-2hrs Characteristics: The object emitted beams, This is a possible UFO abduction case, Entities were seen, Missing time was experienced, Marks found on body afterwards
text:
UFO outside house (only seen from inside) abduction through walls/roof (?) 
 
preface: No, this is not my idea of a joke to waste your time. I have held onto this experience for years and have told only few close friends out of fear of being judged. I am probably going to immediately discredit myself by saying this but at the time I had taken about 100 ug of LSD. I feel like this is very important for me to mention even though I am probably about to be discredited because I have a very big sense that I was "picked out" that night for "research" because of doing it. This was not my first time doing it, and even though the experience horrified me it was not my last because I wanted to see if my brain would ever "go there" again and It hasn't. I am very clearly able to separate the hallucinations from whatever happened to me that night. 
 
The night started at my dad's house. I had just started tripping on the acid I had eaten roughly a half hour before and my girlfriend thought it would be best to move me to her friend's house because I was laughing too hard and we didn't want my dad to question my state of mind. I agree and she drives me to her friend's house on the other side of my neighborhood. Once we both arrive the night played out as normal as it could have for the situation for about two hours. I had brought a dab pen with me and remember all of us sharing that watching to wong foo (or lsd's version of it where time stops and its just a single drag queen frowning in a car staring at you soullessly for an hour(don't do drugs, kids.)) about halfway (at least I think) through the movie I don't know how or why but I go from laying on the bed, to standing in the middle of the staircase with nobody around me. I had been entirely teleported in the blink of an eye. I'm there for maybe five seconds before i'm shot into a different room downstairs in the house, and then eventually I am sucked up out the roof through the corner of the house (It felt like i was turned into gas and sucked through a tube, but I kept flipping and sticking to the sides of the wall like one of those sticky knick-knack guys you throw on the wall.) 
 
From here I am entirely enveloped by a soupy gold/yellow light that would switch from the gold/yellow glow to a more analogue orange glow. I can hear a part of myself say "this is deeply wrong" and I am then shot the image of a face right in front of mine. It was almost humanoid but it was entirely translucent and actually lacked a "face." no eyes, maybe some small indents to indicate a nose or mouth but it as very subtle if it had anything. The face would have horrified me if I saw it in a movie or dream but for whatever reason I stayed entirely calm. As a hospital frequenter (I break bones a lot) I could tell this was some sort of doctors office. the room was small like a patient first room and I could see about two or three more of these entities shuffling around in the background assisting. I was on an operating table of sorts made entirely out of the same light I was enveloped in before. Somehow from here I am able to see the back of my own head and skull outside my body only It doesn't look like my head at all. The only way I could tell it belonged to me is because I saw them start digging a scalpel into the back of the skull and immediately felt the most release of pressure I have felt in my entire life. This was indescribably the most satisfying feeling I have felt in my whole Life and I don't even know what they did. It felt like they had sent a charge of white light through my brain only to remove more white light, like they had purified something. In this state I am sent back into the enveloping light and hear myself once again say "this is deeply wrong." I am immediately transported back to my body, sitting in perfect full lotus pose with my right foot sitting up top. As soon as I look at my right foot I notice a giant white blister on my toe that wasn't there immediately before the experience. I noticed the blister had the same white almost translucent color that the entity from the operating room had. it disappeared within a few days but I couldn't help but worry that contact with the being or the craft I was inside of had exposed me to some kind of radiation/etc. Again, I understand that this will probably be discredited because of my aforementioned illicit drug use but again I strongly feel that I was chosen to be studied/met with at all because of the open state that it allowed me to be in at that time, or to make the story easily discredited (like that one Simpsons episode where Homer got abducted but the aliens drenched him in whiskey so nobody would believe him.) (Again I swear on my mother's life this isn't joke or a made up story.) 
 
when I had returned to my girlfriend at the time and her friend they had asked where I went. they said I wasn't gone for too long but they had just noticed me sitting cross-legged on the floor and got worried about me.

summary: Very large, slow descending green fireball
stats: Occurred : 11/15/2019 21:00  (Entered as : 11/15/2019 9:00 PM) Reported: 12/2/2022 2:09:03 AM 02:09 Posted: 12/22/2022 Location: Arbutus, MD Shape: Fireball Duration: 6-8 seconds Characteristics: There was an aura or haze around the object, Missing time was experienced
text:
Very large, slow descending green fireball 
 
As I stood outside in the dark evening hours of the night in the parking lot facing East I saw a very large, bright green, slow descending fireball appear out of nowhere just on the other side of the trees across the street from where I was standing. It was so large that it appeared to be bigger than the size of the distant moon appears to be to the naked eye. It lasted for under 10 seconds and it was so close that I was sure that I would hear it crash nearby, but it did not make a sound as it soon disappeared on the horizon. Unfortunately, due to reasons unknown to me, I cannot recall the exact date and time or any immediate details surrounding the sighting. Just that I saw it. I also do not know why it has taken me this long to report it, for I have since inquired of many people if they saw it too to no avail. I do, however, remember that COVID-19 errupted very shortly after this event. I have also experienced a very significant, spiritual awareness boost, and was guided by, what seems to have been, subliminal thoughts to enhance my spiritual awakening journey which I developed a much stronger commitment to. I also have been a witness to several phenomenal events in the immediate area after seeing the fireball; such as distinct, picturesque cloud formations in the vicinity of where the firball descened from as well as sudden weather pattern changes which defied our local weather service announcements, on quite a regular basis. Again, I cannot recall the exact month or time but it was, indeed, near the start of the COVID-19 pandemic.

summary: Read in details
stats: Occurred : 12/7/2019 22:00  (Entered as : 12/07/2019 10:00 PM) Reported: 11/11/2022 12:58:20 AM 00:58 Posted: 12/22/2022 Location: , County Offaly Shape: Circle Duration: 8-10 minutes
text:
Read in details 
 
HI, 
 
I was looking up online about identifying UFOS. No video or picture I seen was simular to my encounter. I came across your website where it said to email if I had a sighting. 
 
My sighting happened just as the sun was going down. I came home from work, walked in my front door to where I rolled myself a cigarette inside. I walked out again into the front of my house to smoke my cigarette. 
 
As I walked out from my front door I seen something in the distance in the sky moving towards my direction. No sound, nothing. 
 
As I watched, my body completly froze and what I seen in the distance spotted me. From afar, in a split second it shot right up over my house. 
 
I was unable to move and as I looked up watching. My whole life started to flash before me. The only way i can describe this is how its said to happen where life flashes with a person before they die. 
 
That's exactly what happened at first. The lights were so bright I was unsure of exactly what I was seeing and the size of what I was seeing at that point. 
 
I seen 3 red lights in a regtangular shape. What I seen next looked the only way I can describe, like a chanel on a tv that isn't fully tuned in. Where the image on screen distortes and splits in two till its properly tuned in. It did exactly that. 
 
Looking at the 3 trangular lights I started to see the whole shape of the craft, it was a big circular shape with 3 red lights in a triangle shape on it. 
 
At this point I started to get a really bad feeling in my stomach and in my gut. I never felt something so completely wrong. 
 
A small circle in the middle of the craft started to turn and open. The absoulte fear that came over me ill never forget. 
 
Ive always been a very intutive person. And anyone that knows me would always say that . However, this was a feeling I never ever felt or experienced before. 
 
I knew if I stayed there it was gonna take me. Finally my body had movement and I ran inside in a panic. I panicked so much I was not able to even pick up or hold my phone. 
 
Something in me then said what the hell am I doing?. This is unheard of and a once in a lifetime opportunity. I put myself together as quick and best I could and ran back out. It was still in the same place right above my house. I looked up, I felt it look down on me. Then it shot up into the sky and dissapeared. 
 
I had to leave that house after, as it didnt end there. 
 
With 2 people staying with me after my experience, because I was too afraid to stay there alone. We all witnessed the same terrifying things nights after. 
 
I had a sky light in my room. What we all thought was the moon that we had seen through my sky light way over half an hour of us chatting. 
 
When walking outside on that exact spot I was in before for a cigarette. We each said upon walking out how small the moon was that night. 
 
The "moon" that we all seen in that same spot through my skylight for about an hour at this stage. Suddeny was not the moon anymore. 
 
It shot down from up in the sky right over my house. I started uncontrollably crying bearly able to breath. I didnt even see my friends reactions. 
 
A fighter jet came in that moment and chased it away. I ran so fast leaving my two friends behind running to my parents house 10 minutes away. I never went back to that house after that. 
 
I feel very lucky to have seen what I did. The fear was outweighed by how special I felt with my first encounter. 
 
To see my life flash before me. To be unsure and in a situation unknown. I can honestly say in that very moment and even now to think back on, my heart felt and feels full. 
 
There is only one reason why, and here is where the intuitiveness comes out in me. 
What is real in this world for sure?. I'm not sure anyone can answer that.... 
 
What I can say though, 
 
Is what i seen was 
 
REAL. 
 
What I felt was 
 
REAL. 
 
I seen a part of the world we live in that's real, and I didn't have to die to feel it. 
 
Regards, 
Della L

summary: Black line shaped craft keeping same speed as plane then closed in, changed angle when got closer and reflected sunlight
stats: Occurred : 12/19/2019 15:00  (Entered as : 12/19/2019 3:00 PM) Reported: 12/11/2022 1:28:21 PM 13:28 Posted: 12/22/2022 Location: In flight, TN Shape: Changing Duration: 3 to 5 minutes Characteristics: There were aircraft in the vicinity or aircraft chasing the object
text:
Black line shaped craft keeping same speed as plane then closed in, changed angle when got closer and reflected sunlight 
 
I was a passenger on Southwest flight Nashville to Boston, about 45 min to 1 hour into the flight. I spotted off of the left/north side of the plane, an all-black, flat line shape with some depth, which was keeping the same speed as the plane. It was about 1/4 mile out, at the same altitude which was around 30k feet or above. I watched for 2 to 3 minutes trying to make out the form, then the shape started moving closer to the plane maintaining the same height. Similar to 2 cars on a highway, one moving from the fast lane to the middle, while you're in the right lane. When it got closer, it then changed angles, ducking down lower and when it did, the sun reflected off of the body like a metallic reflection. That was the only moment I saw it go from a black line to another shape which was maybe triangular? I told my husband when he picked me up at the airport and he thought maybe a stealth bomber. But that would have been much bigger, I doubt they would fly it towards a passenger jet, and I don't think it would have a metallic shine to it. This was also a flat line with no visible cockpit area. The weather was clear and dry.

I was testing out the new telescope we got for Christmas, using the attach your phone feature. Upon review of the video we saw a ufo 
 
My family was testing out our new telescope and had attached my iPhone to the lens to see how videos through this relatively inexpensive telescope would turn out. As I was recording one part of the video, I would tap the screen to focus on the moon. As it was focusing on the moon, which we only noticed upon review of the video, an object appears to materialize out of thin air and travel quickly across the screen. Upon zooming in, it almost looks like a bullet hole when you see those slow motion videos shooting through something. summary: Orange ball of light.
stats: Occurred : 1/11/2020 23:00  (Entered as : 01/11/2020 11:00 PM) Reported: 12/4/2022 6:02:52 AM 06:02 Posted: 12/22/2022 Location: Dingwall, Highland Shape: Sphere Duration: 5 to 6 minutes Characteristics: There were lights on the object
text:
Orange ball of light. 
 
It was almost 2 years ago now but at the time didn't know how to or who to report a sighting. I wrote down at the time what I had witnessed and now will share it with you. 
 
15 minutes ago, 2300 hrs, Sat 11th Jan, 2020. Dingwall, Scottish Highlands. Went out to my apartment balcony for a cigarette, was looking towards the West when I saw a bright orange light emerge from the back of the hill about 5 miles away. I at first thought that it was an aeroplane but the light wasn't flashing just a faint pulsing glow. I was waiting to hear the sound of an engine but there wasn't any sound at all. It was difficult to guess what altitude it was flying at, but guessing I would say 2-3 thousand feet. It took about 4-5 minute to pass my view point. I have seen Chinese lanterns before and this was definitely not one, it was travelling at a steady controlled speed. I then came inside to view it from my East facing window for about another 10 to 15 seconds until it just disappeared as if to go behind a cloud, its a clear night and not a cloud in the sky. Really freaked me out. Was very sceptical until now. 
Highlander - 11-Jan-20 @ 11:33 PM.

stats: Occurred : 4/14/2020 02:30  (Entered as : 04/14/2020 2:30 AM) Reported: 10/20/2022 6:45:48 PM 18:45 Posted: 12/22/2022 Location: Beaufort, SC Shape: Triangle Duration: unsure memory loss Characteristics: There were lights on the object, The object landed, This is a possible UFO abduction case, Missing time was experienced, Animals reacted to the event
text:
The craft was hovering in the parking lot silently. It was a triangular shape. It was flashing purple and red lights. 
 
On or about the precise date and time my puppy Axel woke me up to go out for a walk. We were under lockdown orders via the president. Axel went down the back stairs as usual. We went into the darkness of the back path of the apartments. When we arrived at the parking lot. I believed at first we were looking at a drone. I looked and the puppy turned his head towards a craft hovering about 1 foot off the ground. The craft was silent it was about the size of 3 SUV's. The craft was turning quietly. I remember the brilliant colors of the lights purple/ indigo and red. The craft was not a perfect triangle but had rounded edges. The lights flashed faster. I remember a flash like a camera taking a picture of me. The dog and I were on the other side of the parking lot continuing our walk. I had no memory of the craft or where it went. I thought it was a drone but have recently had vivid dreams of the dog and I inside the craft. The beings looking at us. I hope it was just swamp gas and electrical charges. I am a Kindergarten teacher a well read and traveled person/ I am respected in my craft of education and have received a promotion to instructional coach. I do not believe the dog and myself could hold the same hallucination at the same time. we both turned looked and saw.

summary: Craft photographed in 2020 showing construction details in front of rising sun and 53 weeks later photograhed again showing details.
stats: Occurred : 7/12/2020 06:26  (Entered as : 07/12/2020 6:26 AM) Reported: 12/2/2022 12:21:38 PM 12:21 Posted: 12/22/2022 Location: North Myrtle Beach, SC Shape: Other Duration: 11 minutes
text:
Craft photographed in 2020 showing construction details in front of rising sun and 53 weeks later photograhed again showing details. 
 
Two events were recorded photographically at the exact same location 53 weeks apart. The location was at the coastline in North Myrtle Beach South Carolina. Event one occurred at sunrise on July 12, 2020 at 6:26AM. Event two occurred July 19, 2021 at 6:37PM. I only report and talk about sightings that are based on photographic evidence as I did in MUFON report 103691 (09-26-2019 Toledo, Ohio) and MUFON report 114460 (02-05-2021 Ft Myers, Florida). 
Unfortunately, the MUFON system tends to ‚Äòbury‚Äô photos and reports, making retrieval and dissemination to the public difficult. I have been reluctant to file these photographed events on MUFON for that reason. 
Event one was photographed at sunrise at the beach on 07-12-2020 at 6:26AM. The photos are from a collection of about 50 taken with a Nikon 300mm lens, over a period of about 11 from 6:21 to 6:32AM. Photo 1 is a wide-angle view that includes a man walking in the left side of the frame. Photo 2 is a zoomed-in view about one minute prior (6:26AM). Photo 3 is a closer zoom with three circled features as follows. Left Feature: ‚ÄòWater-Tower‚Äô shape. Center Feature: a castle-like merlon projection. Right Feature: Platform with Square Peg. 
Event two was recorded 53 weeks later in 2021 using a high quality android phone and the same features were photographed again on the exact same section of beach. Photo 4 is a cropped version of the original taken on July 19, 2021 at 6:37PM. This late-in-the-day photo has a slightly different view of the same features in the same left to right positions. Photo 5 has highlights circled as follows. Left: ‚ÄòWater-Tower‚Äô shrouded by dense white mini-cloud. Center: Merlon projections obvious. Right: Tall saucer sitting on Square Peg platform. 
I challenge anyone to say that these photos events do not represent the same craft. This ship has the appearance of being not man-made and also probably not of the grey alien variety that usually use very flat vehicles designed for their 40 inch stature. 
I worked for 35years as a product development chemist doing research and development for one of the worlds chemical giants. I have about 10 U.S. patents and authored a couple of personal hobby books in retirement. I have had a life time of trained observation and analysis work behind me. summary: Multiple Lights moving outside our Colorado house for the 2nd night in a row.
stats: Occurred : 10/16/2019 23:30  (Entered as : 10/16/19 23:30) Reported: 10/17/2019 4:55:38 PM 16:55 Posted: 12/1/2019 Location: Colorado Springs, CO Shape: Light Duration: 3 Hours Characteristics: There were lights on the object, The object changed color, There were aircraft in the vicinity or aircraft chasing the object
text:
Multiple Lights moving outside our Colorado house for the 2nd night in a row. 
 
This was the second night in a row we witnessed these lights. My fiance filed one on the 15th. We only noticed the one ufo then, but had speculated there may have been more than one. Last night we witnessed at least 3. The light was once again very subtly moving and changing colors (I saw purple/green/red at various times). There was an instance where a plane or jet flew over the object and it then began to rapidly change colors. I also noticed the light rotate to a point where I was able to make out a bit of a shape. I saw a triangle, though my perception honestly could have been off. I took some video with my phone. This was a particularly starry night. I didn't think I'd be able to catch anything since normally my iPhone can't pick-up the stars at night as the camera is only so good. It did catch this light though and the movements I was catching was truly extraordinary. It was blinking/flashing and moving at speeds/in directions I've never seen any norma! l aircraft moved. It almost looked like something you would see in a video game/computer. Almost like a mouse cursor moving. The main light we saw was to the southwest. At some point while I was recording this light, my fiance alerted me to another UFO just to the Southeast at a bit of a higher elevation. This light was a bit more stationary, but had many similarities to the light I was recording. After we had gone back inside, about an hour later at 2:30 AM, my fiance called me into the kitchen to show me another light to the northeast of our house. I took some more video from my office window at the back of the house and once again I captured it doing some more movements. Unsure what these are but at least one of them gave us the distinct impression that it was investigating or searching for something.

summary: Changes shape, rotates, changes colors, does not move the way any airplane moves.

He knew it wasn't a planet, wasn't a bright star, and didn't look like any sort of plane. A plane actually went by it, I'm sure miles apart in the sky, but from our perspective it was a couple feet. It doesn't seem like something the military would make because of the way it moved. 
 
It was a bright star similar to how bright Venus and Mars is, but it changed to red and blue, which at first we thought was an airplane, but it kept spinning in circles as if it was searching for something, when it was moving to the right it would become elliptical- like it was stretching, moved really slow, hovered and spun around and around. 
 
It would slowly move back and forth, up and down. It even made a zig-zag pattern in the shape of an S, my mom and daughter came out, while it was harder for our daughter to detect the movement, my mother saw it. And was shock no F-16 were up there investigating it. It even got dimmer at one point. And my fiance just checked it again now (01:17) and its further to the right of where it was when we first saw it. We were going to use our daughter's telescope- but couldn't find all the pieces we needed to get a closer look.

summary: A light in the sky with a faint ‚ÄúV‚Äù formation, flashed from red to green quickly and was seen numerous times.
stats: Occurred : 10/17/2019 20:30  (Entered as : 10/17/19 20:30) Reported: 10/19/2019 10:07:02 PM 22:07 Posted: 12/1/2019 Location: Raytown, MO Shape: Light Duration: 21:00 Characteristics: There were lights on the object, There was an aura or haze around the object, The object changed color, There were aircraft in the vicinity or aircraft chasing the object
text:
A light in the sky with a faint ‚ÄúV‚Äù formation, flashed from red to green quickly and was seen numerous times. 
 
On October 17 around 8:30-9:00 at night, me and four other friends of mine took a walk. While we were walking we decided to go on a bridge (can be found on google maps at E 67 Street Raytown Mo) that was nestled next to a brewery and was right above a fairly busy road. 
 
It was pretty normal until one of my friends thought that they saw something in the sky. They described it as a disc like object that had lights on it that flashed from red to green very quickly. This was not an airplane as it was not in the flight pattern and the red light on a plane is always on and never flashes. We all figured that they were just scaring themselves and ignored it. 
 
Then I saw a flashing light in the sky that was also going from red to green but it was to far up to see any outline, before I even said anything about it my second friend of the other 4 saw it with me. We both, almost  simultaneously, said ‚ÄúWhat is that!?‚Äù Of course everyone‚Äôs instinct was to look up at it. Including me and my friend that saw it, 4/5 of us saw the light. 
 
The light continued to flicker until it eventually disappeared. I was thoroughly freaked out and was ready to leave but everyone else was fine so we stayed. Then the same friend that saw it with me and another one (now all of us except one had seen the lights) saw it twice. The first time they saw it it was for a split second and they were the only ones but the second time everyone saw it besides me. 
 
At this point we all had seen it and now we wanted to get to the bottom of it. We all went through the possibilities. It couldn‚Äôt have been a drone because they are loud and can‚Äôt legally go over 500 feet here. It couldn‚Äôt have been a plane because it wasn‚Äôt in any flight pattern and had the incorrect lighting. It could‚Äôve been military equipment because there is a military base around here (this cannot be found on google maps) but it is scary nonetheless. 
 
I then started stalking the sky in search for something else and we all saw it two more times where the same thing happened. I then noticed here that the lights have a ‚ÄúV‚Äù shape so them with duller reds flashing with no green with the main light. Then upon more stalking me and one other friend saw two ‚Äústars‚Äù in a perfect line to each other moving along the sky slowly until we decided to look away and lose track of it. 
 
All five of us saw the same thing over and over again on that bridge and it was not anything I can really rationalize with.

summary: Me and My fiance seen a craft the size of a football field glide silently over the road in front of our car.
stats: Occurred : 2/10/2021 19:00  (Entered as : 02/10/2021 7:00 PM) Reported: 11/14/2022 6:53:42 PM 18:53 Posted: 12/22/2022 Location: Seymour, CT Shape: Teardrop Duration: 10 seconds Characteristics: There were lights on the object
text:
Me and My fiance seen a craft the size of a football field glide silently over the road in front of our car. 
 
This incident happened during the late fall or winter about 2 years ago around 7pm. My girlfriend got put of work at 6pm from stop and shop in seymour Ct amd came home to my mother's house in seymour on culver st right from work which was only a few minutes away driving. When she got home she asked me what I wanted for dinner and I told her I was in the mood for some burgers from my favorite burger place called Valley Burger Shack which is on south main st in seymour only about 5-10 from where we were but it was starting to get late and the place closes at 8pm so I put in the order and we left the house around 7pm. We were heading down south main st towards Ansonia CT with my fiance driving our toyota camry and me in the front passenger seat. It was dark out at this time and the leaves had fallen off the trees at this time of the year. This road is a one lane road going in each direction woth houses to our left and the naugatuck river to our right with woods on the other side of the river with some houses mixed in. We were almost at our destination when a huge shadow started crossing the road in front of us. When I looked up to see some faint lights and a craft the size of a football field was silently gliding over the road above the house to the left heading over the street going over the river to our right. It was so low it felt like I could throw a rock and hit it being just over the top of the tree line. As soon as I spotted it I point up towards it and said to my girl do you see this spaceship to my amazement with her jaw dropped she answered oh my god yes it is huge and so fucking low as she slowed down the car so we could watch this thing slowly creep across the road and over the river and in the direction of Oxford ct. It lasted no more then 10-15 seconds I didnt even try to find my phone because I was in such awe of what we were seeing I was afraid to miss any part of the experience. It was so low we were able to see details the craft. It had no wings and wasn't a triangle or saucer shape. It had a few lights underneath it but they were really faint and dim. If it was farther up you probably wouldnt see the lights. Its shape is hard to describe. The best I could descibe it because it was so big was sorta tear drop shaped and since it was night and we were seeing it from underneath we could tell it was metallic but wasn't smooth it had alot right angles and detail. If I was to pick a craft it mostly looked like from TV is it resembled the Millennium Falcon from Star Wars but 10 times bigger. From other sitings ive seen online this was significantly bigger and different shaped. The only one I seen online that was bigger was the one in Phoenix but that was a triangle sorta boomerang shape. This was solid from end to end. I couldn't believe something that was this big could be so silent or be able to fly at all. When we rolled the windows down to see if we could hear it there wasnt a sound at all not even a stong breeze sound just nothing. like a balloon floating weightlessly over us. Ive seen strange things in the sky before but I never imagined I would be this close to something this amazing.

stats: Occurred : 2/24/2021 13:31  (Entered as : 02/24/2021 1:31 PM) Reported: 12/20/2022 4:48:42 PM 16:48 Posted: 12/22/2022 Location: Virginia Beach, VA Shape: Light Duration: 3-5 seconds Characteristics: There were lights on the object, There was an aura or haze around the object, There were aircraft in the vicinity or aircraft chasing the object
text:
A bright flash of white light from straight ahead that passed directly under our airplane within 3-5 seconds of appearing 
 
In or around February 24th, 2021 at approximately 1330 we were flying a training mission in a U.S. Navy C-2 greyhound flying at approx 10,000‚Äô MSL at N37.00W076.00 on a rough heading of 360 magnetic right at the mouth of the Chesapeake Bay at approx 250 KIAS when a bright white flying object appeared in front of the airplane almost co-altitude. It was white as if it was radiating light and headed right toward our airplane at speeds unimaginable. Within 3-5 seconds it had passed just under our plane and I thought we would collide with the object but the pinpoint precision allowed it to fly head-on just below the belly of our plane. I doubt this was a UAV as the size and speed was not conducive to any I possess knowledge of. The encounter gave me the chills and I had a weird feeling in my stomach afterwards as we continued our flight. Both the other pilot and I recalled the encounter and pondered reporting it to the UAP reporting program which had recently been discussed after the F-18s in our area had sighted UAP‚Äôs recently but we did not decide to report the encounter at that time.

summary: Object was photographed, but not seen at the time the photo was taken.
stats: Occurred : 5/12/2021 17:11  (Entered as : 05/12/2021 5:11 PM) Reported: 11/10/2022 12:16:05 PM 12:16 Posted: 12/22/2022 Location: Belmont, MA Shape: Oval Duration: unknown
text:
Object was photographed, but not seen at the time the photo was taken. 
 
May 12, 2021, my girlfriend photographed a rainbow with an iPhone 10 in three consecutive photos (1 ‚Äì 3). The last photograph (3.) captured a white oval shaped object. 
 
I have included the photos with their descriptions. 
 
Photo Information: 
1. First photo is of the rainbow, zoomed in. 
2. Second photo is of the rainbow, zoomed out. 
3. Third photo is of the rainbow, again zoomed in, but this time however the photo caught an oval shaped object at the top center of the image, which was not seen by the photographer at the time the photo was taken. It was seen only a couple of days later when I examined the photos. 
4. This is simply an enlargement of the oval shape with no adjustment to the color or contrast. It is interesting by the fact that it looks as if there is disturbance in the air above and around the object. 
5. The contrast is boosted in this image, as well I increased the DPI to reduce the pixelization to smooth it out. When I did this, I was expecting to see simply a white shape getting whiter. What really struck me were the colors that were hidden in the bleached-out whiteness of object in the original state. 
6. This photo has the contrast pushed almost to the maximum. 
 
I have no idea what this is, and I have never seen this kind of shape appearing in an iPhone 10 image before, assuming it could be a glitch in the picture. 
 
Assuming it is not a glitch, but an actual object, if I were to interpret the colors in photos 4, 5 And 6, I would say the first photo captured an object as it is falling, leaving a sort of wake in the air above it. 5 Looks like the bottom part of the object is heated up while the top is cooler. 6 is that concept visually enhanced. 
 
If there is further interest in this, I have the original, raw photos with the original metadata which I would be happy to share with you at your request. 
 
Thank you. 
David

text:
I saw either 6 or 7 distinct white lights that kept its spacing the entire time it was visible in the sky 
 
On Sat July 10th 2021 I was sitting on the steps in front of my apartment building talking to my friend on the phone. I happened to look up & that's when I noticed the object. I told my friend I'd call her back & I hung up and got my camera on my phone started. I was facing south towards the city of Allentown Pa and saw what I thought was 1 large circle shape with 6 to 8 white lights that seemed to outline the object. The distance between the lights never changed and were perfectly spaced apart at all times. What I saw did not make any noise at all. Then on the second video I took I started hearing a helicopter coming from off in the distance. It came from my left and continued past the object I was originally videoing. I could hear the helicopter coming from way off in the distance yet this object that was directly in front of me never made a sound. I continued videoing until the light on the end of the building next made a reflection in my videos so that's when I stopped videoing. At the start of video 2 you can hear my voice crack when I speak because I had no idea what I was seeing. Also the local airport is closely. When they depart or arrive they fly directly over my apartment building in a northeast to southwest direction. There is also a hospital south of me where there are medical helicopters taking patients to the trauma center. But this object was going southeast to northwest in direction. There is no need for an aircraft to go in this direction nor do I remember ever seeing anything flying in the direction because there just really isn't any reason to. I am a Navy veteran which doesn't mean I know everything about anything. But I know what I saw that night I have no explanation for. Also in the video you can clearly see the helicopter shining its spotlights over towards the object.

summary: A pillar/prism shaped pitch black object with protrusions seen from the plane.
city: above nature protected area CHKO Krivokl√°tsko
stats: Occurred : 8/19/2021 06:07  (Entered as : 08/19/2021 6:07 AM) Reported: 11/19/2022 6:43:40 PM 18:43 Posted: 12/22/2022 Location: above nature protected area CHKO Krivokl√°tsko, Beroun District Shape: Other Duration: 3 to 4 minutes
text:
A pillar/prism shaped pitch black object with protrusions seen from the plane. 
 
The sighting I am reporting happened on 19th August 2021 (Thursday). Time was around 6. 07 ‚Äì 6. 10/11 am approx and the length of the observation could be around 3 ‚Äì 4 mins. I was actually sitting in the plane - left side by a window. It was flight KL1350 from Prague to Amsterdam ‚Äì regular route (the number of the flight could be different in 2021, the route is still being operated in 2022). 
 
My sighting started right away after we finished sharp ascend from the V√°clav Havel aiport above Prague and did turn to flight more northwestern direction. I remember checking flight route after incident at that time, but unfortunately I did not save any printscreens, but the turn is actually always done above nature protected area CHKO Krivokl√°tsko. 
 
Concretely plane flights over or very near village Bratronice and then continues to slightly turn near dam Kl√≠cava. I also noticed close by to Bratronice is ex rocket military base Bratronice (from information I did found, it is now used by people who like post apo). Closest airport would be the one marked as LKKL. 
 
We were not so hight yet around 1700 to 2000 meters at first, we were keep ascending, but slowly so by the end of observation we could above 3000 meters high. Because it was morning most people were actually trying to sleep. I had a good view to southwestern direction after this turn right after first ascend. The sunrise happened just minutes ago (found out it was 5. 58 am) before we took off so the sky was still red, pink and orange, but more light blue to western direction to the right of my window. 
 
That is when I noticed something black just above the clouds layer extremely far away to the very right of my window view. To my eyes it was just something black, I thought perhaps another airplane. But I took my pair of binoculars ‚Äì 20x50 with me on my vacation as I intended to watch some birds there as well. 
 
I had it in small backpack I did not put into the locker over my head so I could reach it, the pair was under the seat in front of me. I quickly zoomed to see into far distance clearly and made sure I see one image with both eyes. Then I froze. 
 
I couldn‚Äôt believe what I am actually seeing. The first impression was what is even that?!!. There was vertically placed solid pitch black object which resembled to me some sort of a black pillar but with sharp squared edges it seemed - prism. When I first saw it, it was under for me so could see at least upper part which was sharply squared shaped. This object itself looked enormous. I think if I would imagine it in a horizontal position it would be close to length of the fuselage of the plane I was in. 
 
But what was protruding from it made me feel even more astonished. There were some kind of protrusions which I can only compare to tentacles of squid. These were moving in similar fashion to tentacles or those appendages of some bacteria if you look under microscope. Some of them were thinner some of them very thick. I was not able to count how many exactly are there, but they was some space in the air between them so it wasn‚Äôt countless number. 
 
Sometimes they interwined or crossed and then went back to sort of moving in the style mentioned before and hanging under the pillar/prism. Couple times the pillar/prism rectracted them inside into itself and they became invisible. They were retracted gradually, it wasn‚Äôt like they disappeared. 
They looked attached to the pillar/prism. The pillar/prism was hovering most of the time, it slightly went up not being right above the cloud layer anymore so the view for me was now 0¬∞ in the horizont, then it was moving rapidly to right and left and opposite while the ‚Äûtentacles‚Äú got risen up (check the sketch). 
 
Whole this object was completely black, but reflecting sun light. After couple minutes it started moving forward rapidly and keep ascending. It was getting smaller how the distance between me and it was becoming greater. At the end of the observation the angle could be ¬∞15 in the horizont. The pillar/prism never changed its shape and stayed in a vertical position it was very clear I am seeing a solid object. 
 
It disappeared in the distance at very far right side. There were no windows, holes on it. I didn‚Äôt see any marking of any other color. There was no sound but that could be because of the distance and the noise the plane was making. Cannot say if there was any weird odor or interference with electrical devices as this was very far away. 
 
I didn‚Äôt take any picture nor video of it. I looked through my phone quickly but couldn‚Äôt even see it at all. I didn‚Äôt allert any other people in the plane. I logically assumed some people could start to panic or behave unpredictably and the last thing I wanted was a cancelled flight returning to Prague and police coming for me. I have no idea if anyone else noticed, but I don‚Äôt think chance of anyone else being here and having a pair of binoculars with them is high and with naked eyes it wasn‚Äôt discernable at all. 
 
I talked about it only with couple of my friends. Some suggested unusually formed jet contrails but I did check pictures and videos of such phenomenon and can say they look like made from smoke which is something completely different from what I saw. Not even those protrusions were smoke like, they were totally black and with reflection of sun and moving more resembled liquid substance than smoke. Even the way these contrails move is different.

summary: Saw triangular-shaped object with flashing lights in the southern sky at Mesa Verde Park at dusk.
stats: Occurred : 10/18/2019 19:00  (Entered as : 10/18/2019 19:00) Reported: 10/28/2019 8:30:22 PM 20:30 Posted: 12/1/2019 Location: Cortez, CO Shape: Triangle Duration: Characteristics: There were lights on the object
text:
Saw triangular-shaped object with flashing lights in the southern sky at Mesa Verde Park at dusk. 
 
UFO siting 10/18/2019  We were standing on the balcony of our room at the Far View Lodge in Mesa Verde National Park in Cortez, Colorado on October 18, 2019 at dusk, just before 7pm. The hotel is 15 miles inside of the park, so we were very isolated and miles away from all building, street or car lights. The balcony faces south and we had just photographed the sun setting in the west at 6:30pm. After the sun had gone down, yet still light, we were commenting on how dark and clear it was without any buildings or street lights for miles. We looked up and it was not yet totally dark. We commented on the amazing view and the distance we could see. There were no clouds in the sky, as my photos will show, and no stars were out yet. 
 
 My friend and I were looked out and saw 3 lights in the shape of a triangle right in front of us.  It was flashing, then 2 of the lights on one side stopped flashing then quickly disappeared. The one remaining light got brighter then went out completely. I saw nothing else in the sky. No planes, no stars, no clouds. 
 
 My friend and I looked at each other and stated that we had both seen the same thing at the same time. It lasted less than 30 seconds in total.

I saw a huge cluster of lights in the night sky shortly after 10:00 hours. It is difficult to estimate the size of the array but the majority of the "lights" - about 100-150 - were primarily multi-colored (not vivid but soft hues pink/yellow/green/light blues etc) with several white lights - 5-10 - that were much larger in size. The cluster was low on the horizon above the tree-line when I noticed it. I immediately realized the cluster was slowly descending below the tree-line and we could only see the upper portion. The array was still clearly visible and she witnessed it too. She went to get her mom from inside the house but the lights had descended out of sight from our viewpoint.

summary: A 'star' faded and changed into a cigar-shaped object.
stats: Occurred : 11/15/2021 15:30  (Entered as : 11/15/2021 3:30 PM) Reported: 12/6/2022 10:35:57 AM 10:35 Posted: 12/22/2022 Location: Colorado Springs, CO Shape: Changing Duration: 15 minutes (approx.)
text:
A 'star' faded and changed into a cigar-shaped object. 
 
Summary: This incident happened about a year ago - the day could be off by 1 or 2 days. I live in Northeast Colorado Springs at just under 6,800 feet elevation. From my house I have pretty expansive views of the mountains to the west and the skies over Colorado Springs. I had just retired the week prior from my job as a test engineer for GPS satellite control software and was at home. At about 3:30pm I decided to walk around my backyard. It was still about an hour before it even started to get dark (sunset about 5pm), so I was surprised to see what looked like the evening star (Venus or Jupiter), but it was so early, the sun was still visible in the late afternoon. I thought to myself - this is the brightest I've ever seen the evening star appear in the daytime. (Later, about sunset, I saw the actual evening star and it was a different object - it was not visible at 3:30pm). 
The sky was mostly cloudy (I'd say 75% obscured by clouds), not the high wispy ones, but cumulus clouds that obscure the sky. There were openings in the sky between the clouds. I looked to the south and I saw this 'star'- from my location, this placed it about halfway between Peterson Space Force Base and Cheyenne Mountain Air Station. Its position didn't move - as the clouds would come and go moving from right (west) to left (east) the 'star' was still in the same place. After 5-10 minutes the shape changed; it started to get bigger, fade and disperse - it grew in size up to the size of the moon before dispersing. 
After another cloud break it was gone, but in its place was this cigar-shaped white object with a black bottom. I could see no wings or tail. It's possible that it could have been saucer-shaped if it was being seen from a side angle - I couldn't tell. It was not the much rounder tic-tac shape seen in other reported accounts. It appeared to me to be probably above 14,000 or 15,000 feet high because the clouds were also obscuring the upper portion of Pikes Peak, which is 14,115 feet. The clouds kept moving at a pretty good clip from west to east and would repeatedly hide/show the object. At one point, I could see a regular jet flying almost directly behind it from west to east because I could see its contrail - it appeared to be the normal very small size of a jet cruising at 35,000 feet. But this object was much bigger and so had to be much closer. I would say it was about the size of a commercial airplane fuselage as it would appear at 15,000 feet; however, it didn't move. For it to be a plane, it would have to have been flying directly into the wind at the exact same speed as the wind in order for it not to move - not likely in my opinion. 
I thought - what a perfect location in which to spy down on one side to see Cheyenne Mountain and the other side to spy down on Peterson. It was there for at least 5 minutes and Peterson didn't launch any fighter jets to chase it. (Most of the time I can hear those louder jets take off from Peterson, but I didn't hear any). Again, I thought this thing must be visible on Peterson's or NORAD's radars, so if they didn't chase this thing, it must either be 1) some kind of known military object or 2) other object not thought to be a threat; otherwise, they would have chased it or something. They didn't. Then after another cloud break, it was gone completely. I never saw it move - it just disappeared from its location.

summary: 4 different UFOs. Perceived through a hunch?
stats: Occurred : 12/8/2021 20:05  (Entered as : 12/08/2021 8:05 PM) Reported: 12/13/2022 9:47:13 PM 21:47 Posted: 12/22/2022 Location: Warren, OH Shape: Triangle Duration: No more than 40 minutes Characteristics: There were lights on the object, There were aircraft in the vicinity or aircraft chasing the object
text:
4 different UFOs. Perceived through a hunch? 
 
I'm a freelance artist. Been living here for 30 years. A few military installations are nearby. Lots of C-130s. Back in '92, there was a mass sighting in my county. A police chase was the focal point of it. 
In the afternoon preceding these events, I was outside doing chores and having a smoke. The wind was powerful and was blowing a range of clouds all about. There's a clearing across from my home, andI was admiring the way the shadows were moving. Then, the shadows parted in such a way that it looked manufactured. I thought to myself, "Man, seems like good cover for UFOs n such." when the weather is wild. 
I went out to have a cigarette later that day. Facing North, I see some sort of aircraft rising at a steep angle, obscured by what trees remain from the housing developments. It turns left, heading south. It remained hard to make out until it passed out of my periphery; lots of trees. It was indeed triangular in shape. No sound, no lights, same color as the sky. A mix of streetlights and moonlight. Crystal clear night. 
I went inside to get mittens and returned moments later. I lit another cigarette and gazed up at a satellite that happened to cut right along my roofline. Totally normal, save for the orange ball bouncing about it. It felt playful; mocking the satellite it seemed. 
Those two events took about 20 minutes. No more than 10 more minutes pass when I see a brilliant white light coming from the East way above me heading West. Then, it dropped suddenly, hundreds if not thousands of feet until it was tugged back upwards, as if on a fishing line. It began to bob and drift out in front of me(facing North). It was triangular in form, one prominent strobing light on the "back" of it. Like a game of Pong, bouncing back and forth. The shape of the craft was triangular, reminiscent of a futuristic race car to me. I could perceive no sound. It drifted off back East, and up a forested hill. 
The next night, 2 AM. I'm having a smoke. I gaze up to the left. I see the shade of an aircraft, one red and one white light. I think nothing of it. That is until the lights jettisoned off in opposite directions, and the craft carrying on through the dark.

Upon closer inspection I realized that the object flying above was not making any noise/sound of any kind. When the object got closer it became obvious it was not a plane. I procured my phone from my pocket to take a picture of it. As I snapped a picture of the object it appeared to have stopped moving. I was surprised by this and then tried to get a second picture of it while it was motionless above me, but my phone started to glitch. In my haste to take another picture I started to just tap at random on my phone hoping to catch what I was seeing. I saw the object come to a complete stop and it became brighter then quickly turned in an upwards position and flew away. It arched up and over flying away from me; then suddenly before it was completely out of sight it turned sharply to the left and disappeared. Leaving an orange/yellow tail behind in its wake. The whole incident took about 1-2 minutes. This was not the first time I had seen this orb of light before, although it was the first time I was able to take a photo of it. I hadn't realized there was a video of it until I looked over my phone pics and became aware that I must of hit the video button in my haste by mistake. The video is about 3 seconds long, although the object is only in frame for about 1.5milliseconds-very fast moving orb of light! If its a man made object it was an amazing sight to see, but if it was unknown to mankind then it was incredible!! Either way what I saw was interesting and exciting to see.

summary: Slow moving light across sky, that flickers and dissappears
stats: Occurred : 1/29/2022 18:20  (Entered as : 01/29/2022 6:20 PM) Reported: 11/13/2022 12:43:31 PM 12:43 Posted: 12/22/2022 Location: Webster city, IA Shape: Light Duration: 15 minutes Characteristics: There was an aura or haze around the object
text:
Slow moving light across sky, that flickers and dissappears 
 
As we drove home to Fort Dodge Iowa from Webster city Iowa, i noticed what I initially thought was a star. But a star I'd never seen in the night sky before (I'm very familiar with the night sky as I've always wanted to be an astrophysicist or aerospace engineer). And as we drove, I realized that the object was moving slowly across the sky. The object was fairly large, and very, very bright. Bright enough to outshine all but maybe one star in the sky. I told my girlfriend to take a left, and go west down a gravel road. When she did, I told her to stop the car and see if I could get a video of the object. In the video, I held the camera still enough to be able to see it move across the sky. I was paying attention to my screen to ensure a good video, but then I realized I might get better quality if I taped it in the raw camera mode on my phone. So I had stopped the video, switched to raw, and pointed my phone back at the sky. To my surprise, the bright object had seemingly vanished from the sky. That's when I wondered, if maybe I had captured it disappearing on my initial video. When I went and watched, during the last maybe 4 or 5 seconds of the video, you can watch it completely vanish. Before I zoom out, you see it flicker slightly a few times, and when I zoom out, maybe a second before the video ends, you watch the light suddenly go dark, and the object dissappear from view. From what I have seen of satellites, this was way too bright, and was moving way too fast to be an ordinary satellite. I had looked up to see if there were any known comets (even though one that size would have a large tail), or maybe some other sort of astronomical event happening. But my search resulted in nothing but blanks. I didn't know who exactly I could tell, or show my video to. Then I saw an article, with a link to this site. So, I felt like I should tell my story with you all, and maybe even the public should you deem it as significant enough. 
 
In the photo I provided of the map, red is where we were stopped. Yellow is our where we had came from. And blue is the direction of travel of the object. I'm having issues with uploading my video, but would like to present it to someone. If there is and investigator that does decide to contact me, I could send it to him/her or anyone via email if that works better.

summary: I sighted an unusual flying object passing by my home that is unexplained.
stats: Occurred : 5/20/2022 10:40  (Entered as : 05/20/2022 10:40 AM) Reported: 11/12/2022 7:14:22 PM 19:14 Posted: 12/22/2022 Location: South Bend, IN Shape: Rectangle Duration: 5-10 seconds max
text:
I sighted an unusual flying object passing by my home that is unexplained. 
 
Generally, each morning my husband and I sit in our front living room having coffee and he reads aloud to me from a large book of philosophy that we study and discuss. We have many large windows in that room, and I am able to birdwatch and enjoy my coffee while he reads. The sighting I am reporting was on a morning with normal weather, although not particularly bright or dark and overcast ‚Äì nothing out of the ordinary. It was mid-morning and broad daylight. My street runs north and south, and we live on a high hill overlooking much of the neighborhood to the east. We were both seated on a couch by the front windows that face east. I am used to seeing aircraft from the local airport (Michiana Regional) passing over at higher levels and we have also seen helicopters, fighter jets on Notre Dame game days, and of course birds flying over. We have eagles and hawks living nearby that we sight regularly. What I saw was like nothing I have ever seen before, and I have found no pictures online that match anything like what I saw to help me describe it to you. The object I saw was flying much lower than any aircraft I have seen before but it was flying over the treetops of even the tall trees in my yard. I would guess the object was flying at about 300-500 feet above ground at about the same distance from my house to the east, perhaps more, but it definitely was flying between my street and Ironwood Road to the east ‚Äì which is 3-4 blocks away. The object was rectangular in shape (it reminded me of a cell phone, only double in thickness but about the same ratio in length and width). My guess is that its size was at least 50 feet long, 20-25 feet wide, and 8-10 feet thick. The object was flying straight south to north; however, it was rotating in a rather slow and steady controlled flat spin. I noticed the spin by the reflection of light moving on the object's southern edge. The object was medium gray in color, metallic in consistency, with no visible windows, or lights observed. I did not hear any sound associated with the object ‚Äì nothing other than normal household noise such as the air-conditioner, refrigerator, etc. I cannot figure out by what method it was flying. Propulsion couldn't have been the means because it was rotating. It had no blades like a helicopter or any type of protrusions on any side because I saw all 4 sides of it as it passed and rotated. I think it took at least a second for each side to turn away from me. I'm not sure, but I think the object was rotating in a counterclockwise manner. Of course, it happened so fast, and I was stunned trying to figure out what I was looking at so by the time I could say anything to my husband the object had gone out of view behind the large tree in our neighbor's front yard. He did not witness it. I texted my little brother who is in the Air Force and he said he didn't know of any military equipment like what I was describing. My father was very ill at the time, I was focused on that, and I didn't know anyone to report it to ‚Äì it didn't seem appropriate to report to the police, so I decided to forget about it. Obviously, something like that is hard to forget about, and today a friend visited who works in air-traffic control who recommended this sight to report my experience. I'm not sure what good it will do, but now I feel I have done my duty to report it.

summary: Single light, moving across the sky in blinking and swaying motion.
stats: Occurred : 10/21/2019 00:00  (Entered as : 10/21/2019 00:00) Reported: 11/16/2019 6:02:47 PM 18:02 Posted: 12/1/2019 Location: Kingsport, TN Shape: Light Duration: 15 seconds Characteristics: There were lights on the object, There was an aura or haze around the object
text:
Single light, moving across the sky in blinking and swaying motion. 
 
Was outside looking up at the night sky to catch some of the Orionid meteors.  A faint light caught my eye, which resembled a satellite or the ISS going over except for the it's motion and intermediate visibility. 
 
 Another person watching the sky with me confirmed what I saw. 
 
 The object moved in one general direction, but in 2-3 second bursts (fading quickly to nothing) and kind of turned in a short arc to the left, before fading, then turning in a short arc to the right, then fading.  It kept a consistent rhythm with this motion, but upon reappearing was back in the straight path of travel before turning once again off course. 
 
 My initial thought was that an airplane may be going overhead and we were seeing a left wing indicator, followed by the right wing indicator, but the obvious arc motion the object made upon each burst of light really couldn't have been possible if it was only the tip of an airplane wing.  I've also never seen an airplane travel in that path before. 
 
 The object was in view for 45 - 60 seconds as it crossed the sky.  Appeared to be a white/bright blue colored light.

summary: Fast moving object that flew over Hill AFB to Ben Lomond Peak in >10 seconds, and made an abnormal 90-Deg hard turn without slowing
stats: Occurred : 7/4/2022 22:00  (Entered as : 07/04/2022 10:00 PM) Reported: 10/31/2022 8:50:16 PM 20:50 Posted: 12/22/2022 Location: Ogden, UT Shape: Light Duration: approx. 10-13seconds Characteristics: There were lights on the object
text:
Fast moving object that flew over Hill AFB to Ben Lomond Peak in >10 seconds, and made an abnormal 90-Deg hard turn without slowing 
 
Event: 
I was watching fireworks on the back porch with my wife and dogs, and noticed a single fast moving green light traveling from my point of view right to left horizontally that blinked approximately every two seconds, and flew from the direction of Hill AFB (South), and was headed towards Ben Lomond Peak (North). This object flew that distance (approx. 26miles) in less than 10 seconds with zero sound (in between fireworks going off(quiet enough to hear a jet)), no afterburner, and made a HARD 90-degree turn East without slowing down at all. I missed it performing the turn because I was going for my phone to record it(looked away for 
 
Personal Background: 
Served in the Air Force for several years where I worked on various fighters, and deployed with them. I've heard all types of airframe flying insanely fast on station and while deployed, but nothing in my years of service topped how fast, and how mind blowing quiet this "thing" flew at the altitude it was at (just above the mountains). 
 
Abnormalities: 
1) An aircraft that would have been flying the direction this "light" was, would have had a red light on the left wing, and green light on the right wing. Even the F-35 which is stationed at Hill AFB is designed this way, and is not uncommon to see/hear them flying around clear as day in the night time. The wing tip lights are small, bright, and distinguishable, but this "light" was circular, only green, had an odd glare to it, and was fairly large. 
 
2) In between flashes we could not see anything at all, and only knew something was there by the flashing green light. The "light" was flying above the mountains to the East of us, and had the back drop of the sky, so we should have been able to see something. 
 
3) I checked flight radars that night, and the only thing that was flying remotely close was a Cessna that we could see flying towards Ben Lomond Peak, and had a flight path going towards Wyoming. 
 
4) I checked Hill AFB website, and the only flights scheduled were for several F-35s that were supposed to fly over Utah on 3 July the day prior.

text:
I was periodically checking the skies last night for any signs of the Haley Comet or shooting stars. 
 
Because we are so close to the airport And in a big city I already knew the changes were slim. We are quite used to all of the airplane traffic that is constantly buzzing over our skies - and can very easily identify planes and helicopters etc. 
 
Around 1:06AM I went to the backyard to have a seat and check around for some shooting stars - while gazing at the east direction near Orion‚Äôs Belt and clear where incoming planes come to land I saw a bright elongated vertical shaped light.  I immediately thought it was wierd bc it was not moving and atill changing form.  I watched it for a few minutes before it‚Äôs shaped turned more circular -and moving lights.  Rapidly moving lights. 
 
The object in the sky did not move and was flashing all kinds of lights - purple blue green red white - I decided it was bizarre enough (now with no planes landing AT ALL -usually one lands ever few minutes)  To run inside and grab the binoculars.  I have a pretty decent pair and what I was able to see was a small circular shape with crazy lights flashing furiously.  I took a few videos as well. 
 
Upon gazing at the sky some more -it appeared there were 6 other mysterious crafts around the eastern skies - these ones were not flashing colors and not nearly as low as the other craft.

text:
Rainbow colored plasma lights  appear  in  southeastern sky seen from Mt. Tamalpais  foothills 
 
Multiple rainbow colored plasma star like objects show up the night before the fires start in Northern California.  These lights were colors all melted together into one yellowish orange purple undefineable color.  This is possibly the most lights I have ever seen on one night.  The night of 10-21-19 was almost exactly the same in number of objects seen.  Extreme heat and clear visibility during these sightings.One witness saw a triangle formation of bright lights moving swiftly to the southeast and did not want to stick around to see anything else.There were multiple sightings of pairs of these rainbow colored lights with the object on the left slightly higher up than the one on the right.At one point in a pair of lights sighting the object on the left plummeted straight down behind the hill while the other continued to hover and expand in shape for about 2 minutes and then shrink down to a tiny dot.A stunning amount of lights were also seen on the night of 10-27-1! 9 at around 11:45 P.M. when there was still a total power blackout in effect in this area of San Anselmo-Kentfield Mt. Tamalpais area.

text:
Triangular object with flashing lights seen by high-school teacher and university student 
 
The object was triangular and had bright lights underneath, with three red lights. It appeared to hover for awhile over Lake Nosbonsing before slowly moving across the lake towards land. It was a large craft and it was flying much too low to the ground to be an airplane. As it flew over us, it wasn‚Äôt as loud as you would expect it to be and it made an odd noise (you could hear a rumble, but more of a whirling noise). As it passed over our home, it seemed to pick up speed and move off quickly into the distance towards Ottawa. 
 
I captured a number of pictures of it (in one it actually looks oval and in the other, its shape looks different). 
 
My son was the other witness to it. He is a full-time Criminal Justice student and I am a respected high school teacher with twenty-two years experience.

summary: Star like shapes moving and then forming a conveyor like line in sky. ((NUFORC Note:  "Starlink" satellites?  PD))
stats: Occurred : 10/23/2019 05:20  (Entered as : 10/23 05:20) Reported: 11/24/2019 10:02:35 AM 10:02 Posted: 12/1/2019 Location: Glendale,  Shape: Formation Duration: 5 Characteristics: There were aircraft in the vicinity or aircraft chasing the object
text:
Star like shapes moving and then forming a conveyor like line in sky. 
 
Leaving for work early on Saturday I left my front door and immediately noticed there were much more stars out than normal (maybe 25-40 more) which drew my attention to the sky. I realized not only were there more stars but they were moving erratically back and forth for 2-3 seconds. They drew in closer and then almost instantaneously they formed into a straight line and started moving from the southwest sky towards the Big Dipper (northwest) like a conveyer belt. It reminded me how traffic would look on a freeway in a single lane. They were not equal distance Sparta and moved each at different speedsI tried to keep count but there was more appearing from what looked like nowhere. At least 70-100 total continuously headed toward the Big Dipper and then disappeared into the sky. It took up the entire span of the sky and lasted for 5 minutes. I could tell this was fat and not in our atmosphere. I woke my wife up to see the event as well. After roughly 8-10 min! utes the event ended and I could no longer see anything.
